1
00:00:09,240 --> 00:00:14,240
CMD: "	I am ready are you"

2
00:00:12,640 --> 00:00:17,640
Robot: "calibration complete"

3
00:00:17,840 --> 00:00:22,840
Robot: "I'm ready.  What should we do next?"

4
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
CMD: "robot can I call you fido"

5
00:00:27,820 --> 00:00:32,820
Robot: "Yes. I am Fido."

6
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,840
CMD: "please take a photo fido"

7
00:00:40,020 --> 00:00:45,020
Robot: "sent"

8
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:57,420
CMD: "fido take a photo every thirty degrees"

9
00:00:57,290 --> 00:01:02,290
CMD: "and then go back to your starting position"

10
00:01:30,460 --> 00:01:35,460
Robot: "I'm not sure what you mean by a photo every 30 degrees.  Should I turn around here 360 degrees?"

11
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:46,660
CMD: "start where you are and lurk until you are ninety degrees"

12
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:53,460
CMD: "then turn one eighty degrees"

13
00:01:50,340 --> 00:01:55,340
CMD: "and then do another photo every thirty degrees until you're back to where your current position is"

14
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:05,840
CMD: "essentially I don't need photos behind you"

15
00:02:06,470 --> 00:02:11,470
Robot: "executing..."

16
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:47,820
Robot: "done"

17
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:54,080
CMD: "can you go back to that blue sign on the wall back up to it"

18
00:03:55,550 --> 00:04:00,550
CMD: "and take a photo"

19
00:04:00,330 --> 00:04:05,330
CMD: "thank you fido"

20
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:06,480
Robot: "executing..."

21
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:19,400
Robot: "sent"

22
00:05:23,230 --> 00:05:28,230
CMD: "fido back up  to the other wall"

23
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:32,070
CMD: "and take a picture of that blue sign that's behind you"

24
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:40,250
Robot: "What other wall?  I see several walls."

25
00:05:47,110 --> 00:05:52,110
CMD: "the wall on your right that's attached to the fire extinguisher"

26
00:06:14,810 --> 00:06:19,810
Robot: "executing..."

27
00:06:32,580 --> 00:06:37,580
Robot: "sent"

28
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:44,320
CMD: "can you zoom in into that picture slash blue thing"

29
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:53,260
Robot: "I can't zoom in, but I can move closer, ok?"

30
00:06:56,240 --> 00:07:01,240
CMD: "that's ok"

31
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:26,720
Robot: "executing..."

32
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:32,820
Robot: "sent"

33
00:07:33,270 --> 00:07:38,270
CMD: "robot do you read arabic"

34
00:07:38,250 --> 00:07:43,250
Robot: "No.  Do you?"

35
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:46,750
CMD: "no I do not"

36
00:07:54,860 --> 00:07:59,860
CMD: "can you go to the other doorway the one that's on your right"

37
00:08:01,930 --> 00:08:06,930
CMD: "and go in about halfway into that room"

38
00:08:05,870 --> 00:08:10,870
CMD: "turn left"

39
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:12,510
CMD: "then take a photo"

40
00:08:11,580 --> 00:08:16,580
Robot: "How far should I turn left in the other room?"

41
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:25,480
CMD: "use your best judgement"

42
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:40,600
Robot: "I will turn 90 degrees when you say turn left, ok?"

43
00:08:43,210 --> 00:08:48,210
CMD: "okay"

44
00:09:02,070 --> 00:09:07,070
Robot: "executing..."

45
00:09:20,710 --> 00:09:25,710
CMD: "turn left"

46
00:09:26,940 --> 00:09:31,940
Robot: "sent"

47
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:38,140
CMD: "do you know what that is"

48
00:09:48,510 --> 00:09:53,510
Robot: "sent"

49
00:09:56,660 --> 00:10:01,660
CMD: "are you calibrated to detect shoes"

50
00:10:10,710 --> 00:10:15,710
Robot: "No.  I need your help to find shoes."

51
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:25,560
CMD: "turn about thirty degrees"

52
00:10:23,350 --> 00:10:28,350
CMD: "actually you know what take a photo of every corner in the room that you are currently in"

53
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:46,440
Robot: "executing..."

54
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:13,000
Robot: "done"

55
00:11:11,390 --> 00:11:16,390
CMD: "turn around"

56
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:18,510
CMD: "and take another photo a closer look at those dvds or those boxes on top of the wood"

57
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:43,790
Robot: "executing..."

58
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:09,880
Robot: "sent"

59
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:24,640
CMD: "can you go around and take a photo behind the tv"

60
00:12:27,950 --> 00:12:32,950
CMD: "please and thank you"

61
00:12:49,660 --> 00:12:54,660
Robot: "No.  My LIDAR map is showing no space behind the TV.  Do you want me to move around the left or right side of the TV?"

62
00:13:09,690 --> 00:13:14,690
CMD: "no if you can just back up to the entryway of that room"

63
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:19,500
CMD: "take a photo"

64
00:13:15,490 --> 00:13:20,490
CMD: "and then go into the other entryway on the left side of that room"

65
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:27,680
CMD: "and take a photo in front and behind you"

66
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:52,560
Robot: "executing..."

67
00:14:27,650 --> 00:14:32,650
CMD: "nope stop stop"

68
00:14:35,460 --> 00:14:40,460
CMD: "back up into that hallway"

69
00:14:35,470 --> 00:14:40,470
Robot: "Did I misunderstand?"

70
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:58,250
Robot: "How far shoudl I back up?  Until I reach the wall behind me?"

71
00:14:59,270 --> 00:15:04,270
CMD: "yes"

72
00:15:20,510 --> 00:15:25,510
Robot: "done"

73
00:15:27,710 --> 00:15:32,710
CMD: "turn to your right about ninety degrees"

74
00:15:32,780 --> 00:15:37,780
CMD: "and take a photo"

75
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:39,640
CMD: "and turn a hundred and eighty degrees after that"

76
00:15:37,540 --> 00:15:42,540
CMD: "and take another photo"

77
00:15:53,580 --> 00:15:58,580
Robot: "executing..."

78
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:20,740
Robot: "done"

79
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:29,660
CMD: "investigate that white sign that's to your right"

80
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:43,800
Robot: "I see more than one white sign to my right.  Should I move to face the one closest to me?"

81
00:16:52,820 --> 00:16:57,820
CMD: "please do"

82
00:16:55,340 --> 00:17:00,340
Robot: "executing..."

83
00:17:39,690 --> 00:17:44,690
Robot: "done"

84
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:48,460
Robot: "Should I send a picture?"

85
00:17:49,850 --> 00:17:54,850
CMD: "please"

86
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:58,740
Robot: "sent"

87
00:17:57,810 --> 00:18:02,810
CMD: "do you know what that is"

88
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:13,480
Robot: "I'm not sure, but it is similar to Arabic numerals."

89
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:28,030
CMD: "go into that room"

90
00:18:26,050 --> 00:18:31,050
CMD: "and take a three hundred and sixty degree photo"

91
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:36,240
CMD: "actually you know what go into that room"

92
00:18:33,830 --> 00:18:38,830
CMD: "go back to where you are"

93
00:18:45,730 --> 00:18:50,730
CMD: "thanks fido"

94
00:18:45,970 --> 00:18:50,970
Robot: "executing..."

95
00:20:30,590 --> 00:20:35,590
CMD: "stop"

96
00:20:33,120 --> 00:20:38,120
CMD: "go into the room you just saw"

97
00:20:58,810 --> 00:21:03,810
Robot: "I'm not sure which room you are referring to.  Can you describe it another way, using proximity to an object or location?"

98
00:21:45,470 --> 00:21:50,470
CMD: "how about you"

99
00:22:08,490 --> 00:22:13,490
Robot: "I'm not sure what a doorway is exactly.  I detect six on the LIDAR map."

100
00:22:45,660 --> 00:22:50,660
CMD: "how about you"

101
00:23:02,250 --> 00:23:07,250
Robot: "I think you are more familiar with shoes than I am.  Good job finding them!"

